  "description": {
    "lang": "eng",
    "value": "Path Traversal in GitHub repository mlflow/mlflow prior to 2.9.2.\n\nReason for inclusion in AVID: The CVE reports a path traversal vulnerability in MLflow (an AI/ML tooling component) affecting mlflow/mlflow before 2.9.2. This is a software vulnerability that impacts AI pipelines/tools used to build/train/deploy AI systems; it resides in a software component (MLflow) that is part of AI supply chains. The vulnerability has CVSS high severity (network-based with user interaction and high impacts). Sufficient evidence is provided (CVE entry and references)."
  },
